trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle"></xref> objects in the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en mängd <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle"> </xref> objekt i den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The GridTableStylesCollection contains <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle> objects that allows the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid> control to display a customized grid style for each <xref:System.Data.DataTable> in a <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.
trans-unit.target: GridTableStylesCollection innehåller <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle>objekt som kan du <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid>Visa en anpassad rutnätet stil för varje <xref:System.Data.DataTable>i <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</xref:System.Data.DataSet> </xref:System.Data.DataTable> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle>

trans-unit.source: On the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid> control, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid.TableStyles%2A> property returns the GridTableStylesCollection.
trans-unit.target: På den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid>styra den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid.TableStyles%2A>-egenskap returnerar GridTableStylesCollection.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid.TableStyles%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid>

trans-unit.source: By default, the GridTableStylesCollection does not contain any <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle> objects.
trans-unit.target: Som standard GridTableStylesCollection inte innehåller något <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle>objekt.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle>

trans-unit.source: Instead, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid> displays each table using default settings for color, width, and formatting.
trans-unit.target: I stället de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid>visar varje tabell som använder standardinställningarna för färg, bredd och formatering.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid>

trans-unit.source: All columns of each table are displayed.
trans-unit.target: Alla kolumner i varje tabell visas.

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle> is added to the collection, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid> uses the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A> to determine which object supplies the data for the grid.
trans-unit.target: När en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle>läggs till i samlingen av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid>använder den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A>att avgöra vilka objekttyper som tillhandahåller data för rutnätet.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle>

trans-unit.source: For example, if the data source is a <xref:System.Data.DataSet> that contains three <xref:System.Data.DataTable> objects, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A> must match the <xref:System.Data.DataTable.TableName%2A> of one of the objects.
trans-unit.target: Om datakällan är till exempel en <xref:System.Data.DataSet>som innehåller tre <xref:System.Data.DataTable>objekt, den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A>måste matcha den <xref:System.Data.DataTable.TableName%2A>av ett av objekten.</xref:System.Data.DataTable.TableName%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A> </xref:System.Data.DataTable> </xref:System.Data.DataSet>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A> does not match any of the <xref:System.Data.DataTable.TableName%2A> values, the default settings will be used to display data for each table, and the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle> settings will be ignored.
trans-unit.target: Om den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A>inte matchar någon av de <xref:System.Data.DataTable.TableName%2A>värdena, standard inställningarna används för att visa data för varje tabell och <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle>inställningarna kommer att ignoreras.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle> </xref:System.Data.DataTable.TableName%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > Always create <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridColumnStyle> objects and add them to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection> before adding <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle> objects to the GridTableStylesCollection.
trans-unit.target: > [!CAUTION] > Alltid skapa <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridColumnStyle>objekt och lägga till dem i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection>innan du lägger till <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle>objekt till GridTableStylesCollection.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridColumnStyle>

trans-unit.source: When you add an empty <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle> with a valid <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A> value to the collection, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridColumnStyle> objects are automatically generated for you.
trans-unit.target: När du lägger till en tom <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle>med ett giltigt <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A>värdet i samlingen <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridColumnStyle>objekt genereras automatiskt åt dig.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridColumnStyle> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle>

trans-unit.source: Consequently, an exception will be thrown if you try to add new <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridColumnStyle> objects with duplicate <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A> values to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Därför måste undantag ett om du försöker lägga till nya <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridColumnStyle>objekt med dubblerade <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A>värden till <xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridColumnStyle>

trans-unit.source: Alternatively, clear the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection> using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection.Clear%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Du kan även radera den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection>med hjälp av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection.Clear%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection.Clear%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection>
